{"tid":512441,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有睇過無限住人？","createTime":"2017-12-28T13:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T16:28:59.000Z","uid":371,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7530f04ca5998202a21f6d4938b6248ed5351130","tid":512441,"uid":371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"萬次嘅心結就係殺咗一百個追捕佢嘅無辜官差、幫旗本做嘢殺嘅人同害咗個妹，呢個心結亦隨住幫凜報仇而得到救贖、解脫。咁點解佢仲活到90年後？尸良做咗一年不死人就想死；閒馬永空做咗200年不死人亦都想死，點解萬次繼續生存落去，直到連天津影久、凜都忘記。個八百比丘尼又點解要創造不死人萬次出嚟？有無人可以講下自己嘅睇法？"},{"pid":"1c782aeb46dd643bf6eee91120d2ddf52bda5cbb","tid":512441,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"睇過唔記得劇情"},{"pid":"7e5ad6e675b85ef881f87ba87ec8dc959b9faecb","tid":512441,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"想睇電影版"},{"pid":"62898a76fdc241589f11e40525fb2ece05049281","tid":512441,"uid":371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"沙村廣明淨係描述咗凜嘅心理同成長，但關於萬次，基本上只係寫咗佢嘅過去，連天津影久嘅形象都豐滿過佢。"},{"pid":"c092d7b79fa4812fda9953c853649844f9dbd529","tid":512441,"uid":371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e5ad6e675b85ef881f87ba87ec8dc959b9faecb","tid":512441,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"想睇電影版"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"睇過，人物塑造得太單薄"},{"pid":"eeddb8f9fe2bf53fd2e2e7c34c53c8f07cbaa893","tid":512441,"uid":371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c092d7b79fa4812fda9953c853649844f9dbd529","tid":512441,"uid":371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e5ad6e675b85ef881f87ba87ec8dc959b9faecb","tid":512441,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"想睇電影版"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"睇過，人物塑造得太單薄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"睇過原著嘅話套戲唔算好睇"},{"pid":"609e96b5d8dbf2f9d658a